Package gov.nih.nlm.meme.beans

Class Summary
ActionDetailsBean Container for "Action Harvester" function to view a molecular action report.
ActionHarvesterBean Container for the "Action Harvester" parameters.
ActionReportBean FinderClient wrapper for "Action Harvester" used to to find MolecularActions.
ActionSequenceBean AdminClient wrapper used to perform "action sequences".
AdminClientBean AdminClient wrapper used to perform administrative tasks.
AuxiliaryDataClientBean AuxiliaryDataClient wrapper for accessing metadata.
ClientBean Parent of all other beans, tracks "host", "port", and "mid service" parameters.
ContentViewBean ContentViewClient wrapper used for editing content views.
EditingReportBean ReportsClient wrapper for generating editing report data.
MappingBean  
TestSuiteSetBean AdminClient wrapper used for performing test suites.
VersionBean This bean represents version information in action harvester form.
WorklistLookupBean WorklistClient wrapper for looking up worklist names.
WorkLogBean
